<h3 id="parsing-example">Parsing Example</h3>

<p>Here is a simple <code>h-card</code> example.</p>

<p>HTML with Microformats.</p>

<pre><code class="html">&lt;div class=&quot;h-card&quot;&gt;
  &lt;a class=&quot;p-name u-url&quot; href=&quot;http://blog.lizardwrangler.com/&quot;&gt;Mitchell Baker&lt;/a&gt;
  (&lt;a class=&quot;p-org h-card&quot; href=&quot;http://mozilla.org/&quot;&gt;Mozilla Foundation&lt;/a&gt;)
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>


<p>Will be converted to this JSON by a parser.</p>

<pre><code class="json">{
  &quot;items&quot;: [{
    &quot;type&quot;: [&quot;h-card&quot;],
    &quot;properties&quot;: {
      &quot;url&quot;: [&quot;http://blog.lizardwrangler.com/&quot;],
      &quot;name&quot;: [&quot;Mitchell Baker&quot;],
      &quot;org&quot;: [{
        &quot;value&quot;: &quot;Mozilla Foundation&quot;,
        &quot;type&quot;: [&quot;h-card&quot;],
        &quot;properties&quot;: {
          &quot;name&quot;: [&quot;Mozilla Foundation&quot;],
          &quot;url&quot;: [&quot;http://mozilla.org/&quot;]
        }
      }]
    }
  }],
  &quot;rels&quot;: {},
  &quot;rel-urls&quot;: {}
}</code></pre>


